name: OpenCV 3.3.0
body: OpenCV 3.3 has been released with greatly improved Deep Learning module and lots of optimizations.

name: OpenCV 3.2.0
body: Long-awaited update to OpenCV 3.x release series, with tons of improvements and bug fixes. More details in the [changelog](https://github.com/opencv/opencv/wiki/ChangeLog).

name: OpenCV 3.1
body: The first major update in 3.0 release series. See [changelog](https://github.com/Itseez/opencv/wiki/ChangeLog) for details

name: OpenCV 3.0
body:
OpenCV 3.0 gold has been just released, with lots of bug fixes and some nice improvements!
See http://opencv.org/opencv-3-0.html for details and https://sourceforge.net/projects/opencvlibrary/ for binary downloads.

name: OpenCV 3.0 beta
body: **OpenCV 3.0 beta** is released, with lot's of NEON optimization, better OpenCL performance on Iris & Iris Pro, improved Java bindings, new functionality in [contrib](https://github.com/Itseez/opencv_contrib) and many bug fixes.

name: OpenCV 3.0 alpha
body:
**OpenCV 3.0 alpha** is released, with refined API, greatly improved performance on CPU, transparent acceleration on GPU and tons of new functionality in the new [opencv_contrib](https://github.com/Itseez/opencv_contrib) repository.
(http://opencv.org/opencv-3-0-alpha.html)

name: OpenCV 2.4.9
body:
OpenCV Development Team congratulates CV community with the long-awaited Spring coming and presents the next 2.4 series release for you! 
Welcome to enjoy **OpenCV 2.4.9** and thanks a lot to all who participated.
http://opencv.org/opencv-2-4-9.html

name: OpenCV 2.4.8
body: OpenCV Development Team worked hard and in this snowy New Year eve proudly presents the next 2.4 series release for you! Meet OpenCV 2.4.8 and thanks a lot to all who participated. http://opencv.org/opencv-2-4-8.html

name: OpenCV 2.4.7
body:
To smooth over these rainy autumn days the OpenCV Development Team created the next OpenCV 2.4 series release for you! Enjoy OpenCV 2.4.7 and as usual big thanks to all who contributed in any way.
http://opencv.org/opencv-2-4-7-is-out.html

name: OpenCV 2.4.4
body:
On the first day of Spring the OpenCV Development Team released OpenCV 2.4.4. Big thanks to all contributors who made pull requests on GitHub, sent bug reports and helped us in any other way!
http://opencv.org/opencv-2-4-4-is-out.html

name: OpenCV 2.4.5
body:
If you completed with your April Fool jokes, it's a good time to meet OpenCV 2.4.5 that OpenCV Development Team prepared for you!
http://opencv.org/opencv-2-4-5-is-out.html

name: OpenCV 2.4.6
body:
OpenCV Development Team worked hard in scorching summer heat and has prepared the next OpenCV 2.4 series release for you!
Meet OpenCV 2.4.6 and thanks a lot to all who participated.
http://opencv.org/opencv-2-4-6-is-out.html
